# Docs

Use this directory for governed implementation support documents.

Recommended contents:

- `ac<N>-<slug>.md` for acceptance criteria (sequential N, kebab-case slug; see `ac-template.md`)
- `editing-cycle.md` for repo workflow rules
- `editing-guidelines.md` for editorial and structural guidance
- `release.md` for release ceremony and conventions
- reference notes that support editorial decisions

Keep these docs aligned with the repo's actual workflow and structure.
